, <a href="/web/20180712202129/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0032520&amp;fLockTerm=Polymerase+Chain+Reaction">Polymerase Chain Reaction</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712202129/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0199231&amp;fLockTerm=Screening+for+venereal+disease">Screening for venereal disease</a>
, <a href="/web/20180712202129/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_MTH_CUI=C0036899&amp;fLockTerm=Sexual+Abstinence">Sexual Abstinence</a>
